ing rates using a time-weighted average of the premium/discount between perpetual and spot prices over the 8-hour period. Funding payments occur automatically at settlement times, with long positions paying short positions when rates are positive. The exchange applies a ±0.75% funding rate cap to prevent extreme payments. Position sizes above 100,000 USDT may experience partial fills during volatile funding periods."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
